Package: ctdR
Type: Package
Title: ctdR: An R package for the analysis Comparative Toxycogenomics data
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Luigi Corsaro [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Luigi Corsaro <lcorsaro69@gmail.com>
Description: ctdR is an R package for the analysis of gene set data. It executes the GSEA of Chemicals as defined by the Comparative Toxicogenomics Database (CTD) website. It also parses the CTD donwloaded data.
